{"tid":1950042,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（選舉戰）一齊做超區選民！附教學","createTime":"2020-03-30T05:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T13:19:19.000Z","uid":163448,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9401a4caa5d373d48a5d617a9caffd1a1afded71","tid":1950042,"uid":163448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:27:06.000Z","msg":"首先，點為之超級區議會嘅選民<br />\n原來你只要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不是功能組別</span></span>你就有資格做超區選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />基本上人人都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有資格，都要填form的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n表格link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2ceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1172f88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHr9r9S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHr9r9S.png&h=6a0d43c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係功能介別到揀(2)區議會第二功能界別<br />\n基本上你填呢份野，之後fax去28911180就有多一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以踢走李慧琼同周浩鼎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwQqKYd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwQqKYd.jpg&h=f4ec089c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bccafc500a9bfc4db505be23ab3bb9161991f029","tid":1950042,"uid":163448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:27:25.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2aa2a713aa6330b5ac04366f0ab303778cb245","tid":1950042,"uid":163448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T